at i Tobago]] [[Trinitat i Tobago]] (2) * {{TUR}} (51) * {{URS}} (295) * {{URU}} (32) * {{VEN}} (36) * {{Bandera|South Vietnam}} [[Vietnam]] (8) * {{CHI}} (59) * {{XIN}} (1) {{Final columnes}}
